text:
Time to Get Organized! ✔️ Hop on over to BabiesRUs.com where they are offering up some nice discounts on Koala Storage Bins . In addition, they are also on sale Buy 1 Get 1 40% off , making for some HOT buys! Choose free in-store pickup (if available near you); otherwise, shipping is free on orders of $19 or more.
Here are a few deal highlights:
Koala Baby 2-Pack Storage Bins – Natural with Coral Printed Liner 
Only $9.98 (reg. $24.99) – just $4.99 per basket!
* Buy 2 and pay just $15.96 total – ONLY $7.98 per 2-pack of bins – just $3.99 per bin! 
Koala Baby 2-Pack Storage Bins in Coral/Burlap OR navy blue 
Only $12.98 (reg. $19.99) – $6.49 per bin!
* Buy 2 and pay just $20.76 total – ONLY $10.38 per 2-pack of bins – just $5.19 per single bin!

Koala Baby Ombre Paper Twist Basket – Pink OR Blue 
Only $4.98 (reg. $9.98)
* Buy 2 and pay just $7.97 – ONLY $3.99 per basket! 
Koala Baby Ombre Jute Round Bin – Pink OR Blue 
Only $9.99 (reg. $19.99)
* Buy 2 and pay just $15.98 for both – ONLY $7.99 per round bin!
